    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You are the Mayor of Stinkytown.</strong></h2>Your town stinks after a bit of a downward spiral you've experienced lately.<br>It is time to clean up your land because even the greatest mayor can't live in stink indefinitely.<br><br>Solve puzzles, manage energy and clean your surroundings in Stinkytown, a small puzzle game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SOLVE PUZZLES</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042810/extras/e99e145fc93f6534dd2c9ba8dc20245f.avif?t=1725009727\" width=620 height=170 /></span><br><br>Find puzzles around the house, and use various methods to solve them.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>INTERACT WITH OBJECTS</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042810/extras/937f7512d631ebd3834c9e95975ebbae.avif?t=1725009727\" width=620 height=170 /></span><br><br>Some objects have lore, discover them all while doing your mayorly duties.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CLEAN AREAS</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042810/extras/41101611c676af50561613a17898ef3a.avif?t=1725009727\" width=620 height=170 /></span><br><br>Bring colour back to your house, and take out the trash. It's good for your mental health!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TAKE A NAP</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042810/extras/5eac4e2bde7d2cb1570811704985dbda.avif?t=1725009727\" width=620 height=170 /></span><br><br>Even the bravest mayor needs a nap sometimes. Recover energy to continue your journey.<br><br><br><br><i>Coming Soon!</i>",
